claim: The Evil Queen has been portrayed live by an entertainer.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The Queen has since been voiced by Eleanor Audley , June Foray , Janet Waldo , Eda Reiss Merin , Louise Chamis and Susanne Blakeslee , and was portrayed live by Anne Francine  (  musical  )  , Jane Curtin  (  50th anniversary TV special  )  , and Olivia Wilde  (  Disney Dream Portraits  )  , Kathy Najimy  (  Descendants  )  , and in an alternative version , by Lana Parrilla  (  Once Upon a Time  )  .
